description:
The Under Network is a website dedicated to discovering and encouraging art,music,philosophy,critical thinking and more. You can always discover something new at our website at www.theundernetwork.com free of censorship and copyright.

WWW.THEUNDERNETWORK.COM

This website is mostly a non-profit organization that strives to present excellent quality art,music,gaming,philosophy,knowledge and much more which have been solely based on objective principles. My website only exists to store,record,share and to preserve peoples works over the internet and share with the rest of the world.

Please share and seed so others may enjoy the best that this world has to offer and so an artists work will continue to live on for generations to come!
